   Research and Evaluation

     * Research Overview: The Board of Corrections' (BOC) approach to
       information gathering, research and evaluation activities.
     * Research Team: Photos and "mini-bios" of the members of the BOC's
       Research Team.
     * Research Data Confidentiality Policy
     * Qs and As: Common questions posed to the Research Team about its
       information gathering activities.
     * Selection and Training Standards Research: Research activities
       related to the selection and training of local corrections
       personnel.
     * Grant Program Evaluation: Research efforts related to the Juvenile
       Challenge Grant Program, Mentally Ill Offender Crime Reduction
       Grant Program, and Repeat Offender Prevention Project.
     * Links: Sites of potential interest to those involved in local
       corrections research. Under Construction
     * BOC Grant Proposal Process [new.gif]

